title: Meek Mill Previews New Record With Young Thug
text:
Home > Music > Meek Mill Previews New Record With Young Thug Meek Mill Previews New Record With Young Thug 0 0 Posted by Kevin Goddard , Mar 21, 2017 at 09:41pm Meek Mill & Young Thug have some new heat on the way. Oh boy, it looks like Meek Mill & Young Thug have a new record on the way. A new clip has surfaced online today via Meek Mill’s fan page that previews a 54-second song from the two superstars being played at the club. While you can’t hear Meek’s verse in the clip, fans can definitely hear Thugger go off on the untitled track, and it sounds pretty fire. Unfortunately, there’s no information on the record like what it’s called or what project it’ll be living on, but who knows maybe it’ll see life on Meek’s long awaited Dreamchasers 4.5 project? Either way, the collab is sounding like it's going to be a problem whenever it does drop. Check it out for yourself (below) and let us know what you think?
